<h2>Dalhousie Guided Video Real Estate Tour</h2>
<p>What's it Like Living in Dalhousie &mdash; An Agents Guided Dalhousie Community Video. Learn a bit about the people, the places, the shops and the life that makes living in Dalhousie special.</p>
<p>Named after the 9th Earl of Dalhousie George Ramsay, the community in Dalhousie was established back in 1967. Dalhousie is one of the most scenic residential neighborhoods in North West Calgary and is bordered by the Sarcee Trail on the west, the Crowchild Trail on the south, the Shaganappi Trail on the east and the John Laurie Boulevard on the north.</p>
