<h3>Dalhousie &mdash; Excellent Location</h3>
<p>One of Calgary&rsquo;s more mature neighborhoods, the community in Dalhousie enjoys an impressive central location with close proximity to top-notch educational institutions, recreational venues, shopping complexes and even the University of Calgary.</p>
<h4>Dalhousie real estate is quite popular considering the neighborhood&rsquo;s unique location and its proximity to several conveniences and amenities.</h4>
<p>Perched on a gentle hill slope, Dalhousie is popular for its picturesque landscaping, winding streets, walking trails and countless green spaces including parks and playgrounds, that render it one of the most desired residential communities in Calgary.</p>
