<h4>About Madeleine D'Houet School</h4>
<p>A family focused school, Madeleine D'Houet offers a faith-based french immersion curriculum for students in grades 7 - 9.</p>
<p>This school also offers a late french immersion program, which allows students to receive billingual education starting in grade 7. Madeleine D'Houet offers a robust athletics program which includes cross-country running, volleyball, wrestling, basketball, danceworks, badminton, flag football, as well as track and field programs.</p>
<p>Serving both full and late French immersion, the Madeleine d&rsquo;Houet School is a junior high serving grades, 7, 8 and 9.</p>
