<div class="cmty-school__content">
<h4>About St. Luke School/&Eacute;cole St. Luke</h4>
<p>&Eacute;cole St.Luke is the only french - immersion elementary school for Arbour Lake students. It also serves other Northwest Calgary communities including &lt; a href=/edgemont.php"&gt; Edgemont &lt; /a&gt; and &lt; a href="/varsity.php"&gt; Varsity &lt; /a&gt;</p>
<p>St. Luke also offers before and after school care as well as an enhanced kindergarten program. A faith-based curriculum focuses on inclusion and building a nurturing community for students, staff, and parents. They also offer a variety of supplementary courses, options, and services through community partners in education.</p>
